{"tid":2013362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：政府為迫泛民盡快通過國歌法 決定將產假法案當「人質」","createTime":"2020-05-12T09:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T11:01:11.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f1a36983255eec3b20ecd1fb7589d72e9e8fd3","tid":2013362,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"據報，政府有意將《國歌法》二讀辯論排在有關延長法定產假的《2019年僱傭（修訂）條例草案》前，客觀效果是威脅民主派要先通過《國歌法》，泛民批評林鄭「政治凌駕民生、真正攬炒之母」<br />\n<br />\n目前距離立法會會期完結只剩兩個多月，法案如果未能及時通過，將會失效。張建宗呼籲，立法會抓緊時間，按建議在餘下任期處理立法程序。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員譚文豪回覆《蘋果》時批評林鄭政府用政治凌駕民生，是真正「攬炒之母」，斥政府將《國歌法》排在延長產假法案前審議，如同將延長產假的法案當成「人質」，脅迫民主派一定要盡快通過《國歌法》，如此做法香港市民一定看在眼內。<br />\n<br />\n詳情 : <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200512/5CMBO6U7TICL6OC25OAZHNQP7Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200512%2F5CMBO6U7TICL6OC25OAZHNQP7Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=5ddae657\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200512%2F5CMBO6U7TICL6OC25OAZHNQP7Y%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=91bd14cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200512/5CMBO6U7TICL6OC25OAZHNQP7Y/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"f7c0be7a0c040696be9d320e2eb343d215b0f8e0","tid":2013362,"uid":179882,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"依次又考驗泛民決心，議會攬炒最佳例子<br />\n利申你反對產假法案都不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dccd79f895c5d38a1191c843b4d3b64384f66f1c","tid":2013362,"ui